snippet.title: Kaia's Ascent | Official Steam Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Kaia's Ascent on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2786290/Kaias_Ascent/

Run, climb, and charge punch your way out of the deep, dark abyss in this exhilarating first-person 3D parkour platformer!

Music: Requiem - ChozoFS - Kaia's Ascent OST
